-- E4 Target Program: greet-shout
-- A trivial two-cell program for the metacircular evaluator test.
-- Used as the target in Experiment 4 (Round 14).

вҠў greet
  given name вүЎ "Alice"
  yield message
  вҲҙ Write a greeting for В«nameВ».
  вҠЁ message mentions В«nameВ»

вҠў shout
  given greetвҶ’message
  yield loud
  вҠў= loud вҶҗ uppercase(greetвҶ’message)
  вҠЁ loud = uppercase(greetвҶ’message)
